{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Meeting_at_Roark_s_House",
  "title": "A Meeting at Roark's House",
  "summary": "At his home in Capital City, the bruised Corporate Sector Authority executive Roark briefs VicePrex Simone Drake on a confrontation with the New Republic over their captured prisoner, General Han Solo. Roark recounts being threatened and struck by a Wookiee during a tense orbital meeting, after which a ship attacked the planet, and the two agree to arrest the Wookiee, secure his grounded vessel, and consider faking a transfer of Solo to lure the New Republic away. During the discussion Roark offers Simone the vacant office of Prex, which she accepts. Imperial liaison Lieutenant Colonel Russel then arrives and pledges the Empire's full assistance, urging an all-out assault on the New Republic ships and the sabotage of the Wookiee's vessel, though Roark insists on following legal procedure for Solo's trial despite Russel's suggestion to bypass it. The meeting closes with arrangements made to contact Admiral Canis, hold the trial on industrial Bonadan, and proceed against the New Republic presence, after which Russel departs and Simone takes her leave.",
